      <div class="row">
        <div class="project-title project-pad">
          Signature Pick
        </div>
        <div class="project-type project-pad sm-space">
          <h2>Designer Furniture E-commerce Website</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row j5">
        <div class="col-sm-8 xs-space">
          <h3 class="xs-space">Overview</h3>
          <div class="sm-space">Signature Pick is the e-commerce offshoot of Redsoul, a design house/metal shop specializing in working with designers to develop unique furniture, accessories and art. I was tasked with designing and implementing an online presence to present and offer their products directly to the public. This included creating a brand identity, designing and developing an e-commerce site, product photography, and social media management.</div>
          <div class="sm-space"></div>
          <h3 class="xs-space">Design Goals</h3>
          <div>1. Design an aesthetically pleasing and easy to use e-commerce site that allows customers to discover and purchase handmade designer furniture and home accessories.
          <br /><br />2. Create branding guidelines that can be utilized across platforms and reflect the  brand's identity.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 summary">
          <div>
            <h5>YEAR</h5>
            <h6>2020</h6>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5>DURATION</h5>
            <h6>9 months, <br />30 hours per week</h6>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5>TOOLS</h5>
            <h6>Adobe XD</h6>
            <h6>Adobe Illustrator</h6>
            <h6>Adobe Lightroom</h6>
            <h6>Adobe Photoshop</h6>
            <h6>Shopify</h6>
            <h6>HTML/CSS/Liquid</h6>
            <h6>Later</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <h3 class="sm-space">Process Overview</h3>
